-- Jose Mourinho Extends His Real Madrid Contract Through 2016
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2012-05-22T12:37:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-22/jose-mourinho-extends-his-real-madrid-contract-through-2016.html
Real Madrid coach  Jose Mourinho 
agreed to extend his contract with the team through June 2016,
the Spanish soccer champion said.  Mourinho has coached Real the last two seasons. He said on
April 25 he planned to remain in the role, damping speculation
he could return to former team Chelsea.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  